channel.title: When I press the Quest tab the client freezes
channel.description:
Ok, so i have tested it with owner, admin, mod, and normal player, and everytime i click the Quest tab my client freezes... i just recently got my client compiler working and once it was working (no errors) i guess it changed then... because it was working before. Here is a quick picture of what the CMD says when it freezes [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/zjxk4m.jpg[/img]
If you know whats wrong please help, because i just got the server online now and i dont want anyone to press it and it freeze there client. And when it does freeze i just have to close and reopen. Thanks, Adam.
